<TITLE> Four to die for dowry killing </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Bhola, Sept 22 (bdnews24.com) -- Bhola district and sessions judge court on Monday sentenced husband and his three relatives to death for killing wife over dowry in Monpura Upazila. The convicts are husband Barun Chandra Das and his relatives Nitai Chandra Das, Dulu Rani Das and Ramesh Chandra Das of Sitakunda village. They are all fugitives. Barun along with the others killed his wife Shimul Rani. Judge Mohammad Idris Alam also ordered the convicts to pay Tk 10,000 each in fine. Rani's brother Sanjay Kumar Das filed a murder case with Monpura Police Station after the incident. bdne
